          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Plastic has become so woven into our daily lives, it‚Äôs almost invisible. Grocery run? Too often we reach for a single-use plastic bag. Need a hydrate while strolling? Most of us carry a plastic water bottle. Sitting at a caf√©? That straw is probably plastic, too. The plastic habit remains stubbornly strong‚Äîeven as we better grasp just how harmful it is.</p>",
